IRS990.MissionDesc: THE MISSION OF THE HOBE SOUND COMMUNITY CHEST, INC. IS TO PROMOTE THE SOCIAL AND EDUCATIONAL WELLBEING OF THE ENTIRE COMMUNITY BY FUNDING PROGRAMS AND INIATIVES SERVING HOBE SOUND RESIDENTS IN NEED
IRS990.Desc: THE HOBE SOUND COMMUNITY CHEST ISSUES GRANTS TO OTHER NON-PROFITORGANIZATIONS WHO, THROUGH THEIR SERVICES, ENHANCE THE QUALITYOF LIFE FOR RESIDENTS OF HOBE SOUND. THE SCOPE OF THESE SERVICES MAY BE BASED IN CHILD CARE, EDUCATION, YOUTH RECREATION, FOOD AND SHELTER, OR OTHER AREAS WHICH WILL HAVE A DIRECT IMPACTFOR THE GREATER GOOD OF THE COMMUNITY. THE ORGANIZATIONSUPPORTED FORTY FOUR SERVICE ORGANIZATIONS IN THE CURRENT FISCAL YEAR.HOBE SOUND STRONG START IS AN INITIATIVE ATTEMPTING TO INCREASE THE NUMBER OF HOBE SOUND CHILDREN READY TO LEARN WHEN THEY ENTER KINDERGARDEN. THE CHEST IS AWARDING SCHOLARSHIPS TO QUALITY EARLY LEARNING CENTERS TO CHILDREN WITH ECONOMIC NEED, SUPPORTING COMMUNITY-BASED PROGRAMS FOR CHILDREN WHO CANNOT ATTEND CENTERS, BRINGING ARTS, MUSIC, AND ATHLETIC PROGRAMS TO THE CENTERS, AND HELPING CENTERS BUILD MORE SPACE TO SERVE CHILDREN. THE GOAL IS THAT BY 2025 EVERY HOBE SOUND PRESCHOOLER WILL HAVE A PLACE TO LEARN AND THE MEANS TO ATTEND.

SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE ORGANIZATION'S FORM 990 IS CURRENTLY REVIEWED BY THE PRESIDENT, TREASURER AND SECRETARY OF THE ORGANIZATION PRIOR TO FILING AND IS AVAIABLE FOR REVIEW BY ANY INTERESTED PARTY AT THE ADMINISTRATIVE OFFICES OF THE ORGANIZATION.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: Form 990, Part VI, Section B, line 12c
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: A COPY OF THE POLICY IS GIVEN TO ALL BOARD MEMBERS, STAFF, VOLUNTEERS OR OTHER KEY STAKEHOLDERS WHICH IS SIGNED EACH YEAR OF THEIR TERM. FULL DISCLOSURE, BY NOTICE IN WRITING, SHALL BE MADE BY THE INTERESTED PARTIES TO THE FULL BOARD OF DIRECTORS IN ALL CONFLICTS OF INTERESTS. THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS SHALL DETERMINE WHETHER A CONFLICT OF INTEREST EXISTS, AND IF SO, SHALL VOTE TO AUTHORIZE OR REJECT THE TRANSACTION OR TAKE ANY ACTION DEEMED NECESSARY TO ADDRESS THE CONFLICT. THE INTERESTED PARTY SHALL NOT PARTICIPATE IN ANY DISCUSSION OR DEBATE AS IT RELATES TO THE CONFLICT. HOWEVER, THEY MAY BE PRESENT TO PROVIDE CLARIFICATION UNLESS PROHIBITED BY ANY PRESENT BOARD OR COMMITTEE MEMBER

FINANCIAL INFORMATION CAN ALSO BE OBTAINED THROUGH THE FLORIDA DEPARTMENT OF AGRICULTURE AND CONSUMER SERVICES WEBSITE.
